{"tid":1041614,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"體育數據機構意甲最佳陣容：C.朗拿度條垃圾沒有入選","createTime":"2019-03-01T03:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T08:15:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf285e1464b80307dafcc53d687112d66a80e94","tid":1041614,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/03/01/b/b5f54c91dfaa859ab1af0e5894af8172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F03%2F01%2Fb%2Fb5f54c91dfaa859ab1af0e5894af8172.jpg&h=e026881b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC.朗拿度無緣這份最佳陣容<br />\n<br />\n  近日，知名體育數據機構《Opta Sports》評選出了今季到目前為止的意甲最佳陣容。<br />\n<br />\n  儘管領跑意甲射手榜，但C.朗拿度的名字並沒有出現在這套陣容當中。此外伊卡迪、高列巴尼等球員也同樣落選。<br />\n<br />\n  具體陣容如下：<br />\n<br />\n  門將：漢達諾域治（國米）<br />\n<br />\n  後衛：辛度（祖記）、史堅尼亞（國米）、阿切爾比（拉素）、簡斯路（祖記）<br />\n<br />\n  中場：阿倫（拿玻里）、比真歷（祖記）、法比安-魯易斯（拿玻里）<br />\n<br />\n  前鋒：亞曆杭德羅-高美斯（阿特蘭大）、比亞迪克（AC米蘭）、艾沙拉维（羅馬）"},{"pid":"39e3536dd62abb30fa14e1e36d09a4c72a39b6b3","tid":1041614,"uid":61228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"沙拉維？"},{"pid":"3b3c99a57bf6eb903f6b53628d4a3f99aa40d525","tid":1041614,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"呢d post唔會推過2頁"},{"pid":"539b7604da1b4ea8ff201ed35081203d2ffe12a7","tid":1041614,"uid":58811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"歐聯入最佳陣容咪得喇<br />\n聯賽who care"},{"pid":"b3b189dc3f31155315a71dd69b94172e4bc36e82","tid":1041614,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"539b7604da1b4ea8ff201ed35081203d2ffe12a7","tid":1041614,"uid":58811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"歐聯入最佳陣容咪得喇<br />\n聯賽who care"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /